{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/\u8be6\u60c5\u63d2\u56fe.png?t=1739628355\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u300aAnomalies Detective\u300b</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A psychological horror game with an episodic plot, thrillers and anomalies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a fledgling paranormal detective. After accepting an unusual commission, your fate changes...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will try to explore secrets and find ways to escape in three major scenes: corridors at night, narrow alleys, and infinitely looping houses. Be careful, many abnormal things happened, as if some strange power wants to devour you...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Similar to the &quot;The Exit 8&quot; game, please find the abnormal things in each scene cycle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please pay attention to every detail in the scene, these anomalies are hidden in inconspicuous corners!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 3 chapters in the game, 3 independent Chinese scenes, more than 80 anomalies, some of which are very secret, waiting for your challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are multiple endings waiting for you to explore. When you find all the anomalies, you will unlock the deepest secrets...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Note: Some of the content of this game is driven by sound effects. It is recommended to wear headphones for the best experience.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay demonstration:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/11\u67087\u65e5_00_00_00-00_00_30.gif?t=1739628355\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the scene</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/33